How to update tasks.

Generate a new foo/tasks.txt in the subfolder.

In this folder, run ./run init.txt to load the current
state.

Select the group to load into: 'gr 0'

Update the task list: 'up foo/tasks.txt'

Redistribute over days: 'ds 90'

Garbage collect, remove deleted tasks: 'gc'

Sort tasks by group: 'sr'

Save: 'w'.
